# GPU fast + accuracy profile

Canonical runtime values live in [`../docker/gpu-app.env`](../docker/gpu-app.env)
(loaded by all NVIDIA compose stacks under `deploy/docker/`).

Summary:
- Keep `DIARIZATION_ACCURACY_MODE=true` with VBx/overcluster timeline locks
- Wall time: 10 min (<15 min audio) or 2/3 of audio (>=15 min)
- Turn-guided ASR; beams 4–5 adaptive; full temperature fallback
- Checkbox enhance for diar+ASR (mild NR, speech-focus loudness)
